{"tid":1902940,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"係carousell 遇到個假口罩賣家","createTime":"2020-02-28T15:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T03:49:30.000Z","uid":234461,"like":1,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8b9146f12733806c023d9d34263381ef63844b3f","tid":1902940,"uid":234461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"借account<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說今日上網喺carousell買到假口罩 都知自己蠢㗎啦 於是懷着一絲希望想賣家退返錢比我 點知賣家可以更無恥叫我賣返出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2EW5nmw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2EW5nmw.jpg&h=6aed881d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uEncMOf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuEncMOf.jpg&h=ef6eed9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rv5UZ8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRv5UZ8g.jpg&h=ed58f52a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xW1MRe0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxW1MRe0.jpg&h=44f9c7e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e87Hpz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe87Hpz1.jpg&h=d623d3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GLjiHmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGLjiHmK.jpg&h=ebb71271&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Em3CXU6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEm3CXU6.jpg&h=24c29401&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HyOfKz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHyOfKz7.jpg&h=6c76b0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面交嘅時候淨係check咗入面啲口罩(係我蠢冇check埋盒） 見到佢地白白滑滑都覺得幾掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但交收完之後覺得個口罩盒愈睇愈唔妥 首先個盒殘殘舊舊都情有可原(可能運輸途中壓爛等原因） 但之後發覺個盒又冇expiry day又冇寫通過Bfe Pfe Vfe 側面淨寫埋啲廢話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGUFVP6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGUFVP6.jpg&h=03c204c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5rH897.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5rH897.jpg&h=14f1d7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAFBt97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAFBt97.jpg&h=b2931af6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVin898.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVin898.jpg&h=6e34e92f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTwAKJu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTwAKJu.jpg&h=7f7ce6d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但明明賣家賣口罩嗰到寫明有齊哂Bfe Vfe Vfe!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0h4C4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0h4C4c.jpg&h=f827bdbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都心知賴嘢 於是上網搵究竟Diapro個包裝係咪真係咁 點知喺網上除咗Carousell以外都只見到以下包裝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJvFbqh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJvFbqh.jpg&h=e31e1d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁咪同返個賣家講囉 點知佢竟然話佢用咗幾個禮拜都冇事 叫我自己賣返出去 詳情可以睇返上面啲圖 仲要多多藉口話個盒冇問題 可能改咗包裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 假嘅都比佢講到真咁<br />\n喺你自己都唔可以確認到口罩係真嘅情況下仲要叫我賣返出去 點解可以無良成咁 就算個口罩有3層都唔代表有pfe vfe 真係有人因為呢個假口罩中咗支那肺炎點撚算 開呢個po希望唔好再有人上當啊啊啊！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢而家仲諗住賣比人㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" 